Global Animal Feed Additive Silica Market Insights
Animal Feed Additive Silica Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Animal Feed Additive Silica Market Overview
The Animal Feed Additive Silica market is poised for significant growth, driven by the increasing demand for high-quality animal feed additives in the livestock sector. The global market for animal feed additives was valued at approximately USD 5.4 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 8.2 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.3% during the forecast period. The growing awareness about animal health and productivity is pushing the need for silica as an essential feed additive. Silica supports better digestion, absorption of nutrients, and overall growth performance in animals. Furthermore, rising concerns about sustainable farming practices and natural feed additives contribute to market expansion.

